$interpreted: PAFF: That machine...I remember it was closed previously?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: See, it's just like NEKO said...
Nolva: Wait!
PAFF: Miss Nolva...?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: I was wondering where you and Kittyeyes went. Turns out you made it all the way here too! Nolva-chan is awesome!
Nolva: Umm...That machine, I checked it just now. Looks like it's already broken. No reaction at all.
Nolva: Let's...go back to Roger's home first, okay?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: But, there's this strange light coming out of it? It's the same as Nora-chan's monitor!
Nolva: ...N-no, that's...
Nolva: In short, p-please...don't come over here. Please!
PAFF: Miss Nolva...what's the matter?
Nolva: ...Umm...
Nora: There are some things you don't want us to know, right.
Nora: I've met many people who can lie without even batting an eyebrow. Miss Nolva, you're not one of them.
Nolva: ...I'm sorry...I...
Nora: ... To be honest, I've read some messages from Unit-01. Although it's hard to believe, it does indeed answer all the questions...
Nora: I think, it's the exact same thing you're desperately trying to hide.
Nora: I have to investigate that mainframe in order to confirm whether it's real or not. Apologies... can you please move out of the way?
Nolva: ...No. I...I can't do that...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: W-w-w-wait a second. What the heck are you two talking about?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Why is it that NEKO can't understand a word you're saying!?
PAFF: Same. Miss Nolva, what are you...
Nolva: ....W-wait...AH!
Nora: ...Miss PAFF, back off!!
PAFF: Miss Nolva!?
Nolva: ......
NEKO#ΦωΦ: She fell asleep? So she can fall asleep whenever she wants!?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ha, hahaha...So she wasn't kidding when she said she had a "monster friend"?
Nora: Waverlyde...that is your name, isn't it? I have something to say. Please, calm down first and listen, okay?
Nora: My guess is that you want to help Miss Nolva keep her secret. That's why you suddenly attacked us...right?
Nora: If so, please rest assured. We have absolutely no intention to harm her.
Nolva: ......
PAFF: No...Nora is right.

PAFF: We don't want to harm Miss Nolva.
We just want to know why we came to this world.
PAFF: ...Are you willing to believe us?
PAFF: Thank you...Waverlyde.
PAFF: ...Miss Nolva! Are you alright!?
???: ...I remember you.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Y-y-y-you, who are you? Where'd you come from!
Nolva: Ugh...
PAFF: Miss Nolva, are you alright?
Nolva: ...Eh, w-what just happened? The last thing I remember was that Waverlyde suddenly forced me into a slumber...
Nolva: Don't tell me...did he do something to you guys——
???: That thing took the attack for you. That's why you didn't suffer any injuries.
???: ...This exact same thing happened the last time I defeated it too.
Nolva: I knew it...you and Waverlyde are...
???: ...When I opened my eyes, he was fighting those wooden dolls.
???: I knocked him unconscious, but that action depleted my energy. It resulted in me being unable to fulfill my duty...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Hold your horses! You better give NEKO a clear explanation. Why did you attack Nolva-chan all of a sudden?
???: My memory contains your files. However, judging by what you said, you three seem to not recognize me...
???: No...except you. Looks like you managed to figure it out, at least partially.
???: Am I correct, codename SIGMA?
PAFF: ...Codename SIGMA?
Nora: ...ZERO, GAMMA, SIGMA. This is the core memory code for us three.
Nora: ...It's our name, the name of "marionettes".
Nolva: ......
NEKO#ΦωΦ: W-what the hell are you talking about? Ahahahaha! All this marionette nonsense...NEKO's a human, like really human!
PAFF: Nora, we...we did come to another world, right?
Nora: Unfortunately, judging from the already decrypted messages, we are not the people we think we are.
Nora: We're merely a piece of memory data that has been copied and implanted into very precisely-crafted marionettes. That's all we are.
PAFF: .........M......marionettes...
PAFF: ...This is...us...?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ahahahaha, Nora-Chan, that's a good story you just made-up~ It sounds really creepy and stuff, but NEKO doesn't get scared easily...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Urgahhhhhhh! My head...my head feels like it's splitting open...
Nolva: Everyone...what's going on!?
???: The fact that you are reacting to this energy is the best proof.
???: Even though you only have bits and pieces of the memory data, you are all marionettes, just like me...that's an indisputable fact.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: W-why is this happening...WAHHHHH!
???: You decrypted your own memory data and discovered that your real identity is different from what your appearance suggests. Am I correct?
???: Or, it could be the case that you were conscious about it all this time...?
???: Whatever. I have no intention of diving deeper.
Nora: (The monitor stopped glowing...?)
???: Codename GAMMA, "Neko Asakura".
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ......Me?
???: Back there, you asked me why I attacked that human. Now...you should be able to "hear" the answer to that.
PAFF: ...It's inside our heads...that song...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Is that...what we should do in this world...?
Nora: "Destroy humans"...we can hear it clearly now.
???: Yes. That is our supreme command.
???: I spent massive amounts of energy to reactivate your memory circuits. Now, you've remembered the reason you were born...
???: And now you know, that we are comrades striving to complete the same mission.
PAFF: ......NO!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: A-Aroma-chan!?
PAFF: Miss Nolva, you...remembered all of this, right?
PAFF: You're afraid that we would be sad after learning the truth. That's why you tried to get in the way of our investigation...is that correct, Miss Nolva?
Nolva: After taking the medicine, I saw Waverlyde's memory. That's when I realized...it was me who woke all of you...
Nolva: ...I don't know what I should do...I'm sorry...
PAFF: Miss Nolva, why would I blame you?
PAFF: You've been so kind and considerate to us. You cared for us all this time...I am very thankful, for everything you've done!
Nolva: ...*sobs...*sobs*...
PAFF: Even if everything you said is true, I won't...blindly follow this "command".
PAFF: Perhaps I'm merely a marionette with a memory disorder...but I still want... to decide how I want to live myself...
???: ...I think, I am angry right now.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: That shadow...you're Æsir!?
???: Codename ZERO, you are protecting a target of elimination. You are blocking the execution of the supreme command...
???: I must now prevent you from continuing to operate.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: UGAHHH! My head, my head is gonna crack...
Nora: ...Ugh...such massive energy...
PAFF: ......Miss Nolva, run......
Nolva: This is bad...If this keeps up...
Nolva: ...Ah, Waverlyde!
PAFF: Miss Nolva!?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ouch, that really hurt...Aroma-chan, NOW!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Teehee! We did it!
PAFF: Wait...NEKO, look!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Waahh! This is bad this is bad this is bad...We're screwed!!
???: I'll start with you. I'll take away your core.
PAFF: NEKO! NO!!
Nora: (...As expected...my speculation was correct. Energy, core, the light from Unit-01...)
Nora: (...If that's the case...)
Nora: I understand now. They're "batteries".
Nora: The cores in the three of us will automatically extract energy from this world. Using Unit-01 as the terminal, it is then transferred to you.
Nora: The attacks just now and the self-recovery, they are possible all because of it.
Nora: ...This is the reason why we were produced.
???: I do not understand complicated mechanisms. However, I know one thing: that machine is designed to be a part of you.
???: Destroying it will only result in one thing.
Nora: ......Yes, I know.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nora-chan! What's the matter?
Nora: Only by doing this...can we defeat her.
PAFF: ...But, Nora, you...
Nora: Nora...is the person most important to me...
PAFF: Eh?
Nora: To protect someone important, Nora chose to sacrifice herself.
Nora: I...This unit, will also do the same.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nora-chan!!
PAFF: Wa...WAAHHHH!!
Nolva: How come...
???: Why...why would you protect humans to this extent?
PAFF: You...will never understand.
PAFF: Nora, she...protected us...We will rebel against the command...rebel against you!
